		detail:
			"Supervised by Prof. Katelin Schutz (McGill) and Prof. Joerg Jaeckel (Heidelberg). Fully funded scholarship (CAD 20,500). Research on the Axion Gegenschein effect, culminating in the MSc thesis.",
